claim: Performance (film) features a member of The Beatles.
premise_source_doc_sentence: The fifth Beatle is an informal title that various commentators in the press and entertainment industry have applied to people who were at one point a member of the Beatles , or who had a strong association with the `` Fab Four ''  (  John Lennon , Paul McCartney , George Harrison , and Ringo Starr  )  during the group 's existence .
